item.title: Indiana Jones game will be released in 2024
item.description: MachineGames Unveils First Look at Indiana Jones and the Great Circle - Xbox Direct 2024 This is great news for Indiana Jones fans! The game will be released in 2024, and you can play it on PS5 and Steam.
